data.description: *Motivated Sellers* Look no further! This well-kept 3 bedroom, 3-bathroom home features an open-concept living space that flows from the great room to the kitchen and dining area with a neutral color pallet for a warm welcome. The second floor consists of the primary bedroom, 2nd bedroom, utility room, play room(is being used as a nursey) and a large loft for entertaining.
